---
/**
 * Preloader — home page only. "A slow inhale before the site opens."
 *
 * The KAMU K mark builds itself: the three geometric shapes draw on as
 * hairline strokes (stroke-dashoffset), then quietly fill with ink —
 * a nod to the logo's basic-shape construction. A thin progress line +
 * understated counter track real asset loading underneath. When loading
 * and the draw both settle, a brief beat, then the bone curtain lifts to
 * hand off to the hero (fires `kamu:ready`).
 *
 * Bone ground, ink mark. Calm throughout (~3s feel). prefers-reduced-
 * motion skips the draw and simply fades. Once-per-session lock is
 * DISABLED for review — re-enable before final deploy.
 */
---

